channel.title: I've been gone for a while and need help
channel.description:
Hey everyone, I was on here a long time ago but I couldn't even remember my username so I have a couple of questions about servers.
I read something about a 508 Client or something and I'm just wondering if anyone can tell me and explain to me what it is exactly.
